OL,3,CGovernment promises 'London-style'
OL,4,Cbuses across the country with #1bn
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FThe government has revealed where #1
OL,8,Fbillion in funding will go to deliver
OL,9,FLondon-style buses nationwide as part
OL,10,Fof a massive Budget boost.
OL,12,FTransport Secretary Louise Haigh on
OL,13,FSunday confirmed #712 million in
OL,14,Ffunding for local authorities to
OL,15,Fimprove services, alongside a further
OL,16,F#243 million for bus operators.
