OL,7,FA reformed allocation model has been
OL,8,Fbased on need ` for example an area's
OL,9,Flevels of deprivation and population `
OL,10,Finstead of making areas compete for
OL,11,Ffunding as in previous years.
OL,13,FMs Haigh said the investment would end
OL,14,F"complicated and inconsistent" funding
OL,15,Fmodels that have impacted passengers
OL,16,Ffor years.
OL,18,F"Buses are the lifeblood of
OL,19,Fcommunities, but the system is
OL,20,Fbroken," she said.
