OL,3,CGovernment promises 'London-style'
OL,4,Cbuses across the country with #1bn
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,F"Too often, passengers are left
OL,8,Fwaiting hours for buses that don't
OL,9,Fturn up ` and some have been cut off
OL,10,Faltogether.
OL,12,F"That's why we're reforming funding to
OL,13,Fdeliver better buses across the
OL,14,Fcountry and end the postcode lottery
OL,15,Fof bus services."
OL,17,FThe policy comes alongside the
OL,18,Fgovernment's recent decision to cap
OL,19,Ffares at a maximum of #3 during the
OL,20,Fbudget.
