OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FAn inflationary limit will also be set
OL,8,Fto ensure other fares are not
OL,9,Fautomatically increased to #3. The cap
OL,10,Fwill run until the end of 2025.
OL,12,FSingle bus fares in England have been
OL,13,Fcapped at #2 outside London, where
OL,14,Fthey are #1.75 per journey, for most
OL,15,Froutes since January 2023.
OL,17,FMs Haigh made the announcement as part
OL,18,Fof the Welsh Labour conference that
OL,19,Fwill continue in Llandudno on Sunday.
